Veľa šťastia.

104
00:12:51,662 --> 00:12:53,959
Vždy som tu pre neho.

105
00:12:59,211 --> 00:13:01,547
Lenže on ma nikdy nechce.

106
00:13:59,681 --> 00:14:02,197
Zase si mysľou niekde inde.

107
00:14:04,752 --> 00:14:05,844
Tu máš.

108
00:14:06,119 --> 00:14:07,600
Pre teba.

109
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,603
